result.name: China House

reviews.text: Excellent place to eat not only good Chinese food but you get friendly service. They feature an excellent set lunch menu where you order either a rice or noodle dish plus extras. Fairly priced and recommended
Price a bit high compare with the location/district but food quality is very good
Nice Shanghai cuisine

I have been a customer of this restaurant for past 2 years, having accumulated around 10-20 total visits as this is one of the only upscale Shanghai cuisine restaurant in Tai Po. We are getting bored of the food here as there is little variety in the menu, and the food is overpriced and on the very oily and salty side. I always have a dry mouth after eating from this shop due to the MSG levels.

The customer service has been terrible, hard to find waiters to order or to pay bills and their attitude is awful. Food quality has been deteriorating over the years, it was ok and passable standard when the restaurant first opened. 

I really recommend this restaurant only if you have no other choice.
Nice food here

result.name: 家傳滬曉

reviews.text: 門口招呼並不太友善， 食物質素可以。2019年開始入座起計90分鐘用膳。

Excellent place to eat not only good Chinese food but you get friendly service. They feature an excellent set lunch menu where you order either a rice or noodle dish plus extras. Fairly priced and recommended
晚飯要早d去
Price a bit high compare with the location/district but food quality is very good

地方舒適闊落，食物中規中矩，較同集團另一餐廳「京饌」遜色，尤其北京填鴨比較乾身。

員工尚算友善，但有時很難找到他們的蹤影。我們21:30入座，吃到22:40時怕阻他們收工，員工也表現得不介意。(收23:00)

若非有信用卡優惠或會員優惠，價錢會略貴。

reviews.text: Large mall with interconnected bridges to get to different zones.   Mid range brands mainly.  Nothing extravagant.  Food,  clothing,  supermarket....all sorts
shopping experience is more or less same as in Shatin but more space for walking around......need some seats for old people
Themed pop up stalls were held regularly. Different zones of the mall are linked with roofed bridges. very convenient  to get around even in bad weather.
nice food, reasonable price especially after 2 p.m.
great mall in taipo area with varies retailers and reataurants. good place for spending a day with family.
